HEADWORD: naprapathy
<hw>naprapathy</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A drugless method of treatment
based on the belief that disease symptoms arise from problems with
ligaments and connective tissues.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

